Package org.jboss.windup.reporting.model

Interface ClassificationModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EffortReportModel, com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, LinkableModel, TaggableModel, ToFileModelTransformable, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    public interface ClassificationModel
extends EffortReportModel, LinkableModel, ToFileModelTransformable, TaggableModel
    This classifies files and provides general background information about a specific FileModel. (For instance, an XML file may be classified as a "XYZ Configuration File".) A ClassificationModel may also contain links to additional information, or auto-translated/generated/updated versions of the source file.
